parameters:
\n<Detective>(...!? What... it's the same as before... no, even
more pressure...!)

\n<???>\c[18]Why... did you come back here again? I told
you to stay away from me...

\n<Detective>Damn...! I'm not sure what's going on, but... this
isn't the Luna from earlier...!

\n<???>\c[18]Why... did you come back here...? I told you
to stay away from me...

\n<Detective>There is clearly hostility... I don't think we can
communicate, we need to do something...!

\n<???>\c[18]Why... did you come back here...? I told you
to stay away from me...
\n<???>\c[18]Aria... Aria... why did you come back...?

\n<Detective>Damn... You can still move... My stamina... is
already...!

\n<???>It's okay, Papa. Luna, I remember everything
now...

\n<???>There were times when I felt lonely... but in the
end, you were there with me.

\n<???>Just that was enough to make me happy... Luna, I'm
sorry for saying terrible things back then... I've
always wanted to apologize.

\n<???>It's okay, things like that... I... we... as long
as Luna is happy... if you could keep smiling...

\n<???>I'm sorry, for leaving you behind... You worked
so hard... but I couldn't respond...

\n<???>It's okay, now... We were able to meet like this
again... I made a lot of mistakes... but still,
because we could see each other with just one
glance...

\n<???>...It's true. I mean... But Luna, you've done a
lot of bad things too, so let's get scolded by
Mama together, okay?

\n<???>I'm truly... sorry... This device... will stop
soon... It was only moving based on my thoughts,
so if I disappear, the device will also stop.

\n<Detective>...Yes, exactly. Get along with your daughter... I
will take care of the rest.

\n<???>Hehehe...♥ You're really kind, Uncle. Maybe I've
fallen in love♥
\n<???>What...!? Luna, what on earth is going on!

\n<Detective>Hey hey, stop that in front of your father. You
too, behave mischievously in moderation.
And so, another madman was born from that town.

The city of Sakuhai continued to decline as a city
of madmen, and eventually the government
prohibited entry into it.

In the center of the place where the phenomenon of
madness occurred, a deep darkness still spreads...
